snippet.title: Kumba vs. The Evil Penguin
snippet.description: Kumba vs. The Evil Penguin Puzzle adventure. In a kingdom far away King Kumba needs to find back his kidnapped girlfriend.

snippet.title: Doodle Dino Bowl
snippet.description: Doodle Dino Bowl Let the bowling ball fly as far as possible. Collect the stars and pins to buy upgrades in the shop.

snippet.title: Tofu Ninja
snippet.description: Tofu Ninja Platform game. As a brand new ninja you must collect all stars and make sure to reach your destiny.

snippet.title: Ninja Painter 2
snippet.description: Ninja Painter 2 Puzzle game. Move through the levels and try to paint the stated areas with the right color.

snippet.title: Indi Cannon Players Pack
snippet.description: Indi Cannon Players Pack Arcade game. Use the Indi ragdolls and shoot them away to collect all the golden coins.

snippet.title: Penguins Attack TD 4
snippet.description: Penguins Attack TD 4 Tower defense game. Prevent the penguins from entering your base building towers along the road.

snippet.title: American Racing
snippet.description: American Racing Racing game. Try to become the ultimate american racing champion earning cash to upgrade.

snippet.title: The Mountaineer
snippet.description: The Mountaineer Point 'n click puzzle. Help the mountain climber to reach the top of the mountain using the objects.

snippet.title: Ninja Mafia War
snippet.description: Ninja Mafia War Strategy game. Use your ninja troops to take out the mafia. Earn points to upgrade troops.

snippet.title: Infectonator 2
snippet.description: Infectonator 2 Strategy game. Raise a zombie army and try to infect all people in the world with the zombie virus.
